  ./metadata/com.beachape/enumeratum-circe_3/index.json:9:    "description" : "Enumeratum is a type-safe, reflection-free enumeration library for Scala, and enumeratum-circe adds Circe encoders, decoders, and key codecs for its enum and value enum types. It lets Scala 3 JVM applications serialize and deserialize Enumeratum entries as JSON strings or primitive values while reusing Circe's standard type class APIs.",
